data.description: Attention all horse owners! An exceptional opportunity awaits you to acquire an established horse property featuring stables, pastures, a tack room, and more. Nestled on 4.7 acres of land, this property includes a spacious 3 bed 2 bath home spanning over 2200 sq ft.  Enjoy the benefits of whole-home solar panels, ensuring energy efficiency and sustainability. Additionally, This home has desirable features such as a sunken den, a huge front porch ideal for relaxation, and a charming stone fireplace to create cozy atmospheres, a Spacious Kitchen and dining area and so much more.   Conveniently situated just 23 minutes away from the new Ellabell Hyundai plant, this property offers both convenience and tranquility. Please note that the home is part of an estate and will be sold in "As-Is" condition. Dont miss this rare opportunity to own your dream horse property!
